      "content": "it's just that the support doesn't actually change the reality of it. no matter how much i talk or what i do, the pain is still there tomorrow. it's like i'm just stuck in a loop of suffering. sometimes i look at it and it feels like the only way to actually find some peace is to just... stop. to finally have some stillness. does that even make sense?",
